lead_paragraph: The brothers, who were among three suicide bombers who carried out the Brussels attacks on Tuesday, had violent criminal records.

byline.contributor: Reporting was contributed by Lilia Blaise, Aurelien Breeden, Kimiko de Freytas-Tamura and Alissa Rubin from Brussels, Benoît Morenne from Paris and Ceylan Yeginsu from Istanbul.

headline.main: Ibrahim and Khalid el-Bakraoui: From Bank Robbers to Brussels Bombers

snippet: The brothers, who were among three suicide bombers who carried out the Brussels attacks on Tuesday, had violent criminal records.
